## Key Components
- **App.jsx**: Main application component with navigation state management, URL updates, and section handling
- **Header.jsx**: Clickable header with "HOLISTIC TECH AGENCY" text, navigates to home section
- **Navigation.jsx**: Desktop horizontal nav + mobile burger menu with sliding dropdown, sticky positioning
- **SwipeableImages.jsx**: Swipeable image component with horizontal swipe functionality, touch/mouse drag support, dot navigation, responsive images
- **Content.jsx**: Content component with newspaper-style image layout, drop cap, and section rendering
- **global.css**: CSS constants, font faces, color palette, dark mode support, and utility classes
- **Header.css**: Header-specific styles with full-width mobile support and z-index management
- **Navigation.css**: Navigation styles with sticky positioning, dark mode active states, and mobile dropdown
- **SwipeableImages.css**: SwipeableImages styles with horizontal layout, full-width design, and responsive images
- **Content.css**: Content styles with newspaper image layout, drop cap, and text wrapping

